156
00:09:59,405 --> 00:10:01,404
Tidak bergerak.

157
00:10:01,405 --> 00:10:03,304
Mungkin rusak.

158
00:10:03,305 --> 00:10:06,305
Letakkan paruh burung itu ke dalam gelas.

159
00:10:07,305 --> 00:10:08,305
