sehingga titik fokalnya berubah dan itu disebut hukum Snell.

175
00:11:03,705 --> 00:11:06,204
Ia membuat objeknya jadi berputar.

176
00:11:06,205 --> 00:11:09,404
Artinya, panah itu tidak mengarah

177
00:11:09,405 --> 00:11:12,504
ke pancaran yang kosong di kamar mandi,

178
00:11:12,505 --> 00:11:16,704
tapi mengarah ke kamar di seberang kamar mandi.

179
00:11:16,705 --> 00:11:18,704
Ayo kita periksa!

180
00:11:18,705 --> 00:11:20,304
Ya.

181
00:11:20,305 --> 00:11:22,804
Mungkin Maria tidur.

182
00:11:22,805 --> 00:11:27,304
